# API Contract — Platform Manufaktur BOM (Draft v1)

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Versi kontrak** | 1.0.0-draft |
| **Tanggal** | 4 Juni 2026 |
| **Base URL (rencana)** | `https://api.<domain>/v1` |
| **Format** | JSON (`application/json`) |
| **Auth (rencana)** | Bearer JWT / API Key header |
| **Idempotensi** | Header `Idempotency-Key` pada POST/PATCH |

---

## 1. Prinsip desain

```mermaid
flowchart TB
  Client[ERP / Portal / Mobile]
  API[API Gateway v1]
  Svc[Calculation Service]
  Master[(Master Store)]
  Proj[(Project Store)]
  Client --> API
  API --> Svc
  Svc --> Master
  Svc --> Proj
```

| Prinsip | Deskripsi |
|---------|-----------|
| **Stateless API** | Kalkulasi deterministik dari payload + `masterVersion` |
| **Schema versioned** | `schemaVersion` pada Project (saat ini `1`) |
| **Mirror opsional** | `excelMirror` untuk parity; tidak wajib untuk hitung COGS |
| **Rounding terpisah** | Endpoint `/calculate/round` mengikuti ROUND COMPONENT |

---

## 2. Resource map

| Resource | Path prefix | CRUD |
|----------|-------------|------|
| Projects | `/projects` | CRUD |
| BOM tree | `/projects/{id}/bom` | GET, PATCH |
| COGS | `/projects/{id}/cogs` | GET, POST recalculate |
| Masters | `/masters` | GET, POST import |
| Templates | `/product-templates` | GET |
| Parity | `/projects/{id}/parity` | GET audit |
| Export | `/projects/{id}/export` | POST |

