## 6. Event webhook (rencana v1.1)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant API
  participant Hook as Customer webhook
  API->>Hook: project.cogs.recalculated
  Note over Hook: payload projectId, totalCogs, parityStatus
```

| Event | Payload utama |
|-------|----------------|
| `project.created` | `projectId`, `kode` |
| `project.cogs.recalculated` | `totalCogs`, `deltaPctVsExcel` |
| `masters.import.completed` | `sections`, `skuCount` |

