## 7. Versioning & kompatibilitas

| Header | Fungsi |
|--------|--------|
| `X-Schema-Version` | `1` (wajib) |
| `X-Master-Version` | hash/tanggal import master |
| `Accept` | `application/json` |

Breaking change → `/v2` dengan migration guide.

